        "en": "(1) Introduction of Corporate Identity System (CIS)<br>(2) Corporate Identity System Constitution - Mind Identity (MI)<br>(3) Corporate Identity System Constitution - Behavior Identity (BI) <br>(4) Corporate Identity System Constitution - Visual Identity (VI)<br>(5) Case Study of Corporate Identity System<br>(6) Logotypes and Marks Design<br>(7) Planning of Standard Color<br>(8) Design of Reserved Font<br>(9) Applied Design of Corporate Identity System<br>(10) Corporate Identity Tree <br>(11) Corporate Identity Manual"
